      "trigger": "scene_get_unown_dex",
      "description": "After the player has caught 3+ Unown (EVENT_MADE_UNOWN_APPEAR_IN_RUINS set), a Scientist appears at (11,15). When the player steps on coord (11,14) or (10,15), the scientist walks to the Research Center and the player is automatically warped in to receive the Unown Dex upgrade."
