  "notes": "The Ruins of Alph Outside serves as the hub for all Ruins sub-areas. It connects to four puzzle chambers (Ho-Oh NW, Kabuto NE, Omanyte SW, Aerodactyl SE), the Inner Chamber via a central cave, the Research Center, two Union Cave B1F shortcuts, and gates to Route 32 (east) and Route 36 (north). Water patches near the Union Cave entrances (center-west) support Surf encounters. Grass encounter rate is only 4% — among the lowest outdoor rates. The Ruins are approximately 1500 years old; no one knows who built them or why."
